sync emit.l/eval.l with eval.c algorithms
	eval.l needs to expand and encode like eval.c before emit.l will work

make encode rewrite r-value variables as the value when value is subr

use Context instead of Env to store locals in eval

encode variables as
	direct read/write on GLOBAL var object, or
	indirect read/write on LOCAL var object as level + offset

encoding:	var name -> level & offset | value-cell
runtime:	<array> of values				level & offset | value-cell

Env = {
  level		-> long
  keys		-> <array> { vars... }
  values	-> <array>
  parent
  child
}

Variable = {
  name
  env
  offset
}

Context = {
  parent
  child
  keys
  values
}

